Properties.Caption: Просмотр Мониторинг Станций
Properties.Tag: Select [MON_K_UL].[CUL] As [Организация], Max([MON_K_UL].[NUL]) As [Наименование организации], [MON_K_UL].[INN] As [ИНН пользователя], [MON_K_UL].[D_OPEN] As [Дата регистрации пользователя], [MON_K_STATION].[D_OPEN] As [Дата открытия], [MON_K_UL].[D_CLOSE] As [Дата закрытия], [MON_K_STATION].[CSTATION] As [Код станции], [MON_K_STATION].[TYPE] As [Тип станции], [MON_K_STATION].[INSTAL] As [Инсталляция станции], Max([MON_K_STATION].[FIO]) As [Ответственный станции], Max([MON_K_STATION].[PHONE]) As [Телефон станции], Max([MON_K_STATION].[ROOM]) As [Комната станции], [MON_K_STATION].[CONNECT] As [Связь станции], [MON_K_DEVICE].[CDEVICE] As [Код оборудования], Max([MON_K_DEVICE].[NDEVICE]) As [Наименование оборудования], Max([MON_K_STATION_K_DEVICE].[VALUE]) As [Значение оборудования станции], [MON_K_STATION_K_DEVICE].[OWNER] As [Собственник оборудования станц], [MON_K_STATION_K_DEVICE].[D_GARANT] As [Дата гарантии] From ((([MON_K_UL] With (NoLock) Inner Join [MON_K_STATION] With (NoLock) On ([MON_K_UL].[MON_K_ULID]=[MON_K_STATION].[MON_K_ULID])) Inner Join [MON_K_STATION_K_DEVICE] With (NoLock) On ([MON_K_STATION].[MON_K_STATIONID]=[MON_K_STATION_K_DEVICE].[MON_K_STATIONID])) Inner Join [MON_K_DEVICE] With (NoLock) On ([MON_K_STATION_K_DEVICE].[MON_K_DEVICEID]=[MON_K_DEVICE].[MON_K_DEVICEID])) Where |0 Group by [MON_K_UL].[CUL], [MON_K_UL].[INN], [MON_K_UL].[D_OPEN], [MON_K_STATION].[D_OPEN], [MON_K_UL].[D_CLOSE], [MON_K_STATION].[CSTATION], [MON_K_STATION].[TYPE], [MON_K_STATION].[INSTAL], [MON_K_STATION].[CONNECT], [MON_K_DEVICE].[CDEVICE], [MON_K_STATION_K_DEVICE].[OWNER], [MON_K_STATION_K_DEVICE].[D_GARANT] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр Мониторинг Станций
